## How to compile

This is the code we need

~~~
julia -e 'using Weave; weave("slides.Jmd", doctype="pandoc")'
pandoc slides.md -t beamer
  --slide-level 2
  -o slides.tex
  --template ./template/pl.tex
  --highlight-style pygments
latexmk
~~~

